The Life and Times of Hank Greenberg;;80;;97;;PG;;"The Life and Times of Hank Greenberg" is a humorous and nostalgic documentary about an extraordinary baseball player who transcended religious prejudice to become an American icon. Detroit Tiger Hammerin Hank's accomplishments during the Golden Age of Baseball rivaled those of Babe Ruth and Lou Gehrig.;;Biography,Documentary;;Aviva Kempner;;1999;;Hank Greenberg,Alan Dershowitz,Bob Feller,Charlie Gehringer,Kenesaw M. Landis,Carl Levin,Walter Matthau,Ira Berkow,Sander Levin,Michael Moriarty,Hal Newhouser,Maury Povich,Shirley Povich,Dick Schaap;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_life_and_times_of_hank_greenberg